\id 3JN - Saveeŋ (Tuam dialect) NT -Papua New Guinea 2011 (web 2014) 
\h 3 Yoan 
\toc1 Rau Ite Imin Tol Tau Yoan Iboode 
\toc2 3 Yoan 
\toc3 3Yo 
\mt1 Rau Ite Imin Tol Tau Yoan Iboode  
\mt2 3 Jon—3 John  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1-2 O etag ite Gaius, yau ŋginiiŋ to lupuuŋ to Krisi tau nabood rau tane ilat payo. Yau lolog igheen tsio kat. Pasaa, saveeŋ onoon ilup ghiit tamin eemon wa. Yau nawatagh: Yo uleep poia pa gabua to anunuun. Ve naghe uleep poia pa gabua to anoŋaan paam, o poia. Tauvene naghason Maaron naghe i maata payo, leso moroghooŋ eta igham ghom sov, ve tinim poia mon, ve gabua isov ighur poi payo.   
\s1 Gaius itaghon duduŋai saveeŋ onoon  
\p
\v 3 Toŋvetaz toit siriv tilam, ve tipaesia varum payau tighe yo ukis saveeŋ onoon tuŋia, ve laghooŋ tsio, yo utaghon duduŋaini. Tauta igham ghau lolog poia kat.  
\v 4 Isaav ighe yau nalooŋ tighe natugŋa tau napaghazoŋai zi pa eez to Krisi na laghooŋ toozi iduduuŋ itaghon saveeŋ onoon, ene igham ghau lolog poia iliiv gabua naol isov. \x * \xo 1:4 \xt 2Yo 4\x*   
\s1 Gaius iŋgin poghania yes tau tilaagh pa uraat to Krisi  
\p
\v 5 Etag ite, yau lolog igheen tsio kat. Yau naghit ghom naghe tinim ibees kat pa uraat tsio to ŋginiiŋ yes toŋvetaz to Krisi pa lepoogh toozi. Onoon, tamtamon siriv, muuŋ yo uwatagh zi mako. Eemon saawe tau tilat peria tsio, yo ugham zi toman lolom poia, ve uŋgin poghani zi.  
\v 6 Ŋgar poia tau yo utotoia pazi na, yau nawataghi pasaa, tamtamon toozi siriv tilam ve tipaesia varum ila lupuuŋ to Krisi gha nilooŋa. Tighe yo lolom pazi ve ugham poghani zi kat. Isaav ighe tipaburigin laghooŋ toozi muul, na ughit zi pa saa gabua tau timbool pani na ve uul zi pani. Leso ugham Maaron loolo poia. \x * \xo 1:6 \xt Tit 3:13\x*   
\m
\v 7 Pasaa, yes tipul nugh toozi sorok mako. Yes tilaagh pa votiaaŋ Krisi eeza. Ve yes tau tighur ila to Krisi mako na, zeran tana lolozi pa ghamuuŋ uleeŋ eta ila toozi mako.  
\v 8 Zeran tauvene, iit aat tagham zi toman loloon poia, ve taŋgin poghani zi. Leso itiŋa talup ghiit pa uraat to votiaaŋ saveeŋ onoon.   
\s1 Ŋgar saghati to Diotrepes  
\p
\v 9 Muuŋ, yau nabood saveeŋ siriv pa lupuuŋ tsiam. Eemon Diotrepes tau izuari ghi ighe le imin daaba tsiam na, i izorzoor saveeŋ tsiei.  
\v 10 Tauvene murei, isaav ighe nalat navot tsiam, ene aat navotia ŋgar saghati tooni ivot ighazooŋ. Pasaa, i iŋgalŋgal saveeŋ sasaghati naol payei. Ve tane mon mako. Isaav ighe toŋvetaz siriv to Krisi tighe tilat tigig gham, ene i irau igham zi toman loolo poia mako. Ve isaav ighe tsiam siriv tighe tigham zi, ene paam, i iŋgalsekin zi, ve izirziir zi pa lupuuŋ to Krisi.   
\p
\v 11 Etag ite, lolog igheen tsio kat. Ŋgar saghati tauvene, yo utaghoni sov. Yo aat utaghon ŋgar poia mon. Pa tamtamon tau ighe itaghon ŋgar poia, ene i tamtamon to Maaron. Eemon isaav ighe tamtamon eta ighamgham ŋgar saghati, ene itotoia ighe i ighilaal Maaron irao soone. \x * \xo 1:11 \xt Mbo 37:27; 1Yo 3:6+\x*   
\s1 Ŋgar poia to Demitrius  
\p
\v 12 Eemon Demitrius, tamtamon tisov tipait vaaru. Pasaa, ŋgar tau i ighamghamu na, ene iduduuŋ itaghon saveeŋ onoon. Ve yei paam nipaiti. Ve yo uwatagh: Saveeŋ tsiei, ene onoon mon.   
\s1 Yoan ipasov saveeŋ tooni  
\p
\v 13 Yau leg saveeŋ naol to nasavia payo. Eemon lolog pa bodeeŋni ila rau mako.  
\v 14 Pasaa, lolog ighur naghe malau mako pale taug nalat naghit ghom ve ituru tasavsaav.   
\p
\v 15 Luuma to Maaron aat izaa tsio. Onoon.  
\p Zetaanŋa siriv tau yeŋa nileep sene, tigham aaz poia payo. Ve yo paam, ugham aaz poia tsiei pa zetaanŋa tau tileep izi ta sena. Uwaat ezazi le tisov, ve ugham aaz poia tsiei pazi.   